{"tid":198036,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"公屋建築成本攀升　2020年度每單位料過百萬","createTime":"2017-04-12T08:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T00:38:48.000Z","uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37892d771401707dfe7b21b138236dd21d1fa003","tid":198036,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T08:54:16.000Z","msg":"公營房屋建築成本節節上升。運輸及房屋局指出，每個公屋單位平均建築成本由2015至16年度的619,000港元，預計2020至21年度升至1,063,100港元；居屋則由2016至17年度的1,076,100港元，預計升至2020至21年度的1,163,300港元。房屋協會方面，資助出售房屋每個單位的平均建築成本，由2015至16年度的1,183,000港元，預計2019至20年度升至1,540,000港元。<br />\n<br />\n公屋建築成本<br />\n財政年度 / 每個單位平均建築成本<br />\n2015-16 / $619,000<br />\n2016-17 / $589,100<br />\n2017-18 / $712,500<br />\n2018-19 / $837,500<br />\n2019-20 / $942,200<br />\n2020-21 / $1,063,100<br />\n<br />\n居屋建築成本<br />\n財政年度 / 每個單位平均建築成本<br />\n2016-17 / $1,076,100<br />\n2017-18 / $1,878,200<br />\n2018-19 / $1,178,600<br />\n2019-20 / $1,139,700<br />\n2020-21 / $1,163,300<br />\n<br />\n房協資助出售房屋<br />\n財政年度 / 每個單位平均建築成本<br />\n2015-16 / $1,183,000<br />\n2018-19 / $1,478,000<br />\n2019-20 / $1,540,000"},{"pid":"6556d6aefd1089b3fedad954773fbf4e0667923b","tid":198036,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:56:48.000Z","msg":"私樓400 萬是基本啦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公屋狗住既"},{"pid":"0bcc30fa06451976a9d51b58f9d318fe79180e1a","tid":198036,"uid":10382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T00:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜樓都冇得上"},{"pid":"2a7eeb256334fd00cdd5e344a4faa7cc9b2f1275","tid":198036,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T00:38:48.000Z","msg":"紅底建築商落格落得勁啫"}]}